{"tid":1076360,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"天翼之鍊V4.40私服(台灣SER) 【愛玩天翼】","createTime":"2019-03-24T19:27:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-25T15:00:31.000Z","uid":26954,"like":5,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"69c2e96474872fdfc0f2386859338c23dab33727","tid":1076360,"uid":26954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T19:27:56.000Z","msg":"------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n遊戲特色<br />\n台灣SER<br />\n神捲唔會點爆裝(成功率15%)<br />\n0課起手無問題(刷神捲,剪刀,課金箱獲利高)<br />\n擴充裝備有屬性<br />\n大翅平(400$內有)<br />\n大翅改過數值(令大翅各有特色)<br />\n各人物(除小愛)群體技能加HIT數(刷怪爽好多,尤其小波,那亞)<br />\n每個地圖BOSS均有機會掉落神捲<br />\n有刷寶圖,刷錢圖,副本<br />\n有大愛,小喬<br />\n解決到win10玩天翼LAG既狀況(補丁)<br />\n新創角色身上有升級禮包(有裝送)<br />\n255LV可獲得趕路鞋(跑速10)<br />\n15億經換取神捲<br />\n有人帶升就1個鐘235LV<br />\n<br />\n------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n舊論壇<br />\n <a href=\"http://taleswravergg.imotor.com/index.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftaleswravergg.imotor.com%2Findex.php&d=Peq93FhG%2BXbpjcIFBj2O6dDxg6radaiL0c7rOhjaEfM%3D&h=56d7245a\" target=\"_blank\">http://taleswravergg.imotor.com/index.php</a><br />\n新論壇<br />\n<a href=\"http://rotalesweaver.com/forum.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Frotalesweaver.com%2Fforum.php&d=Peq93FhG%2BXbpjcIFBj2O6dDxg6radaiL0c7rOhjaEfM%3D&h=6e827705\" target=\"_blank\">http://rotalesweaver.com/forum.php</a><br />\n申請帳號<br />\n<a href=\"https://rotalesweaver.site/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Frotalesweaver.site%2F&d=Peq93FhG%2BXbpjcIFBj2O6dDxg6radaiL0c7rOhjaEfM%3D&h=81f0f3be\" target=\"_blank\">https://rotalesweaver.site/</a><br />\n攻略網<br />\n<a href=\"http://tw.shiadream.net/01jieshao/intro.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftw.shiadream.net%2F01jieshao%2Fintro.htm&d=Peq93FhG%2BXbpjcIFBj2O6dDxg6radaiL0c7rOhjaEfM%3D&h=28d460a0\" target=\"_blank\">http://tw.shiadream.net/01jieshao/intro.htm</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://talewiki.com/talewiki.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftalewiki.com%2Ftalewiki.php&d=Peq93FhG%2BXbpjcIFBj2O6dDxg6radaiL0c7rOhjaEfM%3D&h=1c6b3a55\" target=\"_blank\">http://talewiki.com/talewiki.php</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://tw.17173.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftw.17173.com%2F&d=Peq93FhG%2BXbpjcIFBj2O6dDxg6radaiL0c7rOhjaEfM%3D&h=d4313feb\" target=\"_blank\">http://tw.17173.com/</a><br />\n紙娃娃<br />\n<a href=\"http://lyna.sexy/webdoala/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flyna.sexy%2Fwebdoala%2F&d=Peq93FhG%2BXbpjcIFBj2O6dDxg6radaiL0c7rOhjaEfM%3D&h=e417550e\" target=\"_blank\">http://lyna.sexy/webdoala/</a><br />\n贊助愛玩天翼(課金)<br />\n<a href=\"http://rotalesweaver.com/forum.php?mod=viewthread&amp;tid=8&amp;extra=page%3D1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Frotalesweaver.com%2Fforum.php%3Fmod%3Dviewthread%26tid%3D8%26extra%3Dpage%253D1&d=Peq93FhG%2BXbpjcIFBj2O6dDxg6radaiL0c7rOhjaEfM%3D&h=d7744e6e\" target=\"_blank\">http://rotalesweaver.com/forum.php?mod=viewthread&amp;tid=8&amp;extra=page%3D1</a><br />\n主程式(3月23號版本)<br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/1vOiu9-CfOgFELndB4ReQtw9iADRIaGVf/view\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Ffile%2Fd%2F1vOiu9-CfOgFELndB4ReQtw9iADRIaGVf%2Fview&d=Peq93FhG%2BXbpjcIFBj2O6dDxg6radaiL0c7rOhjaEfM%3D&h=6ff6b186\" target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/file/d/1vOiu9-CfOgFELndB4ReQtw9iADRIaGVf/view</a><br />\n怪物掉落表<br />\n大天使翅膀合成公式<br />\n新精煉方式成功率<br />\n課金箱內容<br />\n卡片內容<br />\n擴充強化方法<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1hxWzzynqZe86EU1jgPdIb-89gO9Skeb0Rvl19dhXjqQ/edit#gid=359109894\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fspreadsheets%2Fd%2F1hxWzzynqZe86EU1jgPdIb-89gO9Skeb0Rvl19dhXjqQ%2Fedit%23gid%3D359109894&d=Peq93FhG%2BXbpjcIFBj2O6dDxg6radaiL0c7rOhjaEfM%3D&h=446282af\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1hxWzzynqZe86EU1jgPdIb-89gO9Skeb0Rvl19dhXjqQ/edit#gid=359109894</a><br />\n<br />\n------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n遊戲資訊<br />\n一階覺醒傷害7000上限<br />\n二階覺醒傷害99999上限<br />\n掉寶率100倍(稀有掉落道具,非神卷、剪刀、裝備類)<br />\n經驗30倍<br />\n物價:1E SEED=100T=25HKD<br />\n武器去到240LV<br />\n------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\nLIHKG公會(只有香港人)<br />\n庫爾聚集<br />\n由於防範有台灣臥底入到公會<br />\n請先TG GROUP/遊戲1:1巴打<br />\nTelegram GROUP<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/BMWsFxMhH5OtMLdKorw9ow\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FBMWsFxMhH5OtMLdKorw9ow&d=Peq93FhG%2BXbpjcIFBj2O6dDxg6radaiL0c7rOhjaEfM%3D&h=59986848\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/BMWsFxMhH5OtMLdKorw9ow</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n新手點賺錢?<br />\n當比巴打帶到上235LV就可以去卡雷德進行重點(第1次免費)<br />\n之後就可以打寶合箱<br />\n1.海底洞穴2(1) 那集右邊可以傳送去耳語2 再行左上入海底洞<br />\n海底洞穴2(1) 好多怪 會跌武器(NPC) <br />\n掉落物又可以合箱抽野(3款唔同,每款40個+40萬=1個箱)<br />\n呢個係平民賺錢方法之一<br />\n2.去墓園/黃金沙漠城打剪刀,神捲<br />\n新手用咩裝<br />\n頭:毛線帽(800萬),真呂布,真海盜帽<br />\n面:怪俠(300-400萬)<br />\n甲:190輕甲(若4000-6000萬)<br />\n武器:175武器(公會倉好多)<br />\n盾:食人魚盾6000萬-8000萬<br />\n背部:新手禮包送翼,大普(3300萬,安美城買),大翅,小普<br />\n手:力與美,蟲手<br />\n鞋:紅鞋,新手鞋<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br />\n課金課咩好?<br />\n同GM/台灣買家課金 都係用i7391<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.i7391.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.i7391.com%2F&d=Peq93FhG%2BXbpjcIFBj2O6dDxg6radaiL0c7rOhjaEfM%3D&h=c5efd053\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.i7391.com/</a><br />\n同GM課金 只會有幣買 買完LINE GM 講你7391 ID 遊戲名稱<br />\n佢見到會叫你OFF 之後發送幣去你AC 之後可以去奪旗室右邊換購<br />\n課金箱唔建議 用SEED收平一半<br />\n<br />\n少課嘅 緊係課大翅,V10戒子 幾百蚊就有<br />\n套裝就課真奧裝(頭,面,盾,甲,鞋) 6000T到 1500HKD<br />\n同GM累積課夠10000T送奧丁裝<br />\n同GM累積課夠20000T送真奧丁裝<br />\n同GM累積課夠30000T送V6刀<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------"},{"pid":"8e4122fe91ef62e976f62e477f1651efb7b34427","tid":1076360,"uid":39448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T19:31:52.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"f5798452b60e1123f2df7b515b8e9af1c3075ac6","tid":1076360,"uid":21588,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-24T19:45:41.000Z","msg":"GOOD POST<br />\n好詳細 一齊加入回憶系列<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc6055a0fd0b7693c7c8271a4e5e509de20dd4fb","tid":1076360,"uid":26954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T11:41:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd5190c516aaf9d6c78e2e02c56bfe5077933a9e","tid":1076360,"uid":12019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T17:58:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/26/015722_ce6d6fbc0c035390a58f25a199ff8898.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F03%2F26%2F015722_ce6d6fbc0c035390a58f25a199ff8898.png&h=2636e0ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/03/26/015828_ead24a8dee3f9e67dbf585379ec4c0f5.p