式"},{"pid":"c35c3be167aecb20d5ef7ee693f7380638a57ae6","tid":1076360,"uid":26954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T20:19:29.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"e00a3d20a0af8103fd4adc466ab7d880ce0b7c26","tid":1076360,"uid":114320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T07:06:45.000Z","msg":"而家玩 等我！"},{"pid":"1e2b7d76651ce98a8a4a20d1221a1b62577f9f6a","tid":1076360,"uid":114320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T07:55:24.000Z","msg":"申請左ac 入game話id錯誤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61f045485cfa20a1e2461034de2ed39ab6a9869d","tid":1076360,"uid":26954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1e2b7d76651ce98a8a4a20d1221a1b62577f9f6a","tid":1076360,"uid":114320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T07:55:24.000Z","msg":"申請左ac 入game話id錯誤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T17:45:22.000Z","msg":"申請完可能要等15分鐘到"},{"pid":"e914c1c4f718cc584d33a4dfa7f4924c0a92ae89","tid":1076360,"uid":26954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T17:48:40.000Z","msg":"新手235後可以點發展？<br />\n多謝隨風巴打教學<br />\n<br />\n咁就先入手175武 然後執下錢打下怪<br />\n短期目標<br />\n有色既海帽/冷帽/信物帽/真信物帽<br />\n甲就用住新手甲 或打d輕甲合145 或165<br />\n面用怪俠<br />\n手用住新手手套<br />\n鞋就用住火鞋 <br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n跟住刷90武 或繼續執錢買<br />\n自己去打魔賢 合190武<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n開始刷卷同剪<br />\n合215武<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n再刷剪同卷<br />\n換中翅 再刷卷沖翼「80%」<br />\n呢度可以考慮課合成+20%卷<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;-<br />\n跟住打錢刷卷剪 換seed<br />\n收遠征野 ，再打卷沖佢上做真奧<br />\n「真奧結晶去403打死0 會出，順手刷埋滅晶 第時合240武靠佢」<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;-<br />\n跟住呢合完 甲》盾 〉頭》面〉鞋 5件野<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n就開始打料合240武<br />\n合完240 同 真奧成套 就可以入學啦， 叫做岩岩合完套校服<br />\n合完真奧5件後 可以因應返市場需要 合多2件野真奧甲盾 或頭面啦 ，拎去換雷戒 或V10<br />\n換完 就基本成型啦 <br />\n215/240武器<br />\n真奧頭<br />\n真奧甲<br />\n大翼 金陽/符暝/獠犽 3選1 睇職業<br />\n真奧面<br />\n真奧盾<br />\nV5/V10/雷戒/火戒。 <br />\nV5「全屬+5」V10「全屬+10」<br />\n雷戒「mr def30」 火戒「sh17」<br />\n<br />\n真奧鞋<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n然後就到擴充時間 慢慢刷下夢境 <br />\nV1 全屬+1<br />\n最高V7 全屬+7"},{"pid":"9209dcfdf25012b7f04673bcab703bfa6a420330","tid":1076360,"uid":156886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T20:32:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3df74897446cc87acc27ab066ab418f838a74a3","tid":1076360,"uid":192390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T17:45:40.000Z","msg":"開唔到AC <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19a03907c6a0c2accbc4794b43583670b07ff6b0","tid":1076360,"uid":26954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d3df74897446cc87acc27ab066ab418f838a74a3","tid":1076360,"uid":192390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T17:45:40.000Z","msg":"開唔到AC <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T19:11:40.000Z","msg":"要等15分鐘到<br />\n又更新左版本<br />\n<a href=\"http://taleswravergg.imotor.com/redirect.php?tid=1149&amp;goto=lastpost#lastpost\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftaleswravergg.imotor.com%2Fredirect.php%3Ftid%3D1149%26goto%3Dlastpost%23lastpost&d=Peq93FhG%2BXbpjcIFBj2O6dDxg6radaiL0c7rOhjaEfM%3D&h=0b4b4137\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://taleswravergg.imotor.com/redirect.php?tid=1149&amp;goto=lastpost#lastpost</a>"},{"pid":"ab62c7373c3ed685ff65348c792061c4a53c9c7b","tid":1076360,"uid":156886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-14T03:28:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets